        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "本题$D E//B C$ \n\n\n$\\therefore\\angle1=\\angle2\\because\\angle A=\\angle A$ \n\n△ADE△ABC \n$\\frac{A D}{A B}=\\frac{2}{3}$ 为相似比\n\n\n$\\frac{S_{\\Delta A D E}}{S_{\\Delta A B C}}=(\\frac{2}{3})^{2}=\\frac{4}{9}$ \n\n设$S_{\\Delta A D E}=4x.S_{\\Delta A B C}=9x$ $S_{\\Delta A D E}=4x.S_{\\Delta A B C}=9x$ \n∴$S_{\\square}\\frac{1}{4}\\sqrt{3}D B C E=9x-4x=5x$ $S_{\\square}\\frac{1}{4}\\sqrt{3}D B C E=9x-4x=5x$ \n$\\frac{S_{\\Delta A D E}}{S_{\\Delta E D B C E}}=\\frac{4x}{5x}=\\frac{4}{5}$ \n",
          "block_bbox": [
            281,
            367,
            1983,
            1976
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "5.如图，在△ABC中，点D，E分别在AB和AC上，DE1BC，M为BC边上一点(不与点B，(重合).连AM 交DE于点N.则A ",
